[Event Slot Modifier]
author=LiquidManZero
description=0 - CTC/Increased chance of Critical Hit
1 - BST/Accelerated Boost Gauge
2 - SKL/Bonus Skill Points for defeating enemies
3 - ?/Slot changes to random effect
4 - ETR/Ether damage &amp; recovery increased 50%
5 - T-C/Turn Cancel
6 - NON/No Effect
7 - RV/Reverse: Boost Gauge of target increases if attacked
8+ - garbage
