[Re-enable Debug Menus [View Note]]
author=punk7890
description=Press one of the buttons below when you have control over a character:

*Select for Battle Debug Menu.
*L3 for Script Debug.
*L2 + R2 for Main Debug Menu.
*R3 to disable debug menus (only works in some menus).

For more info on these menus: https://tcrf.net/Xenosaga_Episode_II:_Jenseits_von_Gut_und_Bose
